<div class="row p-3 gap-3 flex-column flex-md-row">
  <div class="col alert alert-info">
    <h3 class="h4 fw-semibold">Copyright notice</h3>
    The copyright law of the United States (title 17, United States Code)
    governs the making of photocopies or other reproductions of copyrighted
    material. Under certain conditions specified in the law, libraries and
    archives are authorized to furnish a photocopy or other reproduction. One of
    these specific conditions is that the photocopy or reproduction is not to be
    "used for any purpose other than private study, scholarship, or research."
    If a user makes a request for, or later uses, a photocopy or reproduction
    for purposes in excess of "fair use," that user may be liable for copyright
    infringement. Stanford Libraries reserves the right to refuse to accept a
    copying order if, in its judgment, fulfillment of the order would involve
    violation of copyright law.
  </div>
  <div class="col pe-0">
    <% if f.object.selectable_items.many? %>
      <div class="selected-items-container">
        <ul data-item-selector-target="selectedItems" data-template="#selectedScanItemsTemplate" data-status-filter="available" class="list-unstyled d-flex flex-wrap gap-2 bg-white m-0 me-3"></ul>
        <div class="text-cardinal pb-1 mt-2">
          <span>Earliest expected delivery: <%= f.object.scan_earliest['display_date'] %></span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="selected-items-container">
        <ul data-item-selector-target="selectedItems" data-template="#selectedScanItemsTemplate" data-status-filter="unavailable" class="list-unstyled d-flex flex-wrap gap-2 bg-white m-0 me-3"></ul>
        <div class="text-cardinal pb-1 mt-2">
          <span>Earliest expected delivery: No date/time estimate</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <template id="selectedScanItemsTemplate">
        <li class="d-flex gap-2 w-100 align-items-baseline" data-content-id="__ID__">
          <span class="item-selector-callnumber-pill bg-light rounded-pill border">
            <span class="callnumber">
              __LABEL__
            </span>
            <button data-action="item-selector#remove" data-item-selector-id-param="__ID__" type="button" class="btn-close py-0 pill-close">
              <span class="visually-hidden">Remove __LABEL__</span>
            </button>
          </span>
        </li>
      </template>
    <% else %>
      <div class="text-cardinal">
        Earliest expected delivery: <%= f.object.scan_earliest['display_date'] %>
      </div>
    <% end %>
    <div class="mt-2">
      <%= f.label :scan_page_range, 'Page range', :class => 'py-2' %>
      <%= f.text_field :scan_page_range, :class => 'form-control' %>
      <div class="form-text">Examples: '1-15, 25-30' or '249-275, Index'</div>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-2">
      <%= f.label :scan_title, 'Title of article or chapter', :class =>
      'required-label py-2' %> <%= f.text_area :scan_title, :required => true,
      :class => 'form-control', :rows => 3 %>
      <div class="form-text">
        Limited to one article/chapter, not to exceed 50 pages or 10% of the
        work
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-2">
      <%= f.label :scan_authors, 'Author(s)', :class => 'py-2' %> <%=
      f.text_field :scan_authors, :class => 'form-control' %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
